{"product_id":"organic-hyaluron-serum-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hyaluron Serum 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIntensely nourishing organic hyaluron serum to deliver long- lasting moisture and to strengthen the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating) and organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), rose hip (anti-inflammatory) and eyebright (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/strong\u003e: Shake well before use. In the morning and evening apply 1-2 drops on the hands and gently tap into cleansed face and neck.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Betaine*, Sodium Levulinate*, Xanthan Gum*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Sodium Anisate, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Citric Acid*, Euphrasia Officinalis Extract**, Rosa Canina Fruit Ex- tract**, Sodium Lactate*, Geraniol**\/***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (93,2%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49092215341383,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hyaluron-serum-50ml-505516.jpg?v=1739897339","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/organic-hyaluron-serum-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}